<tr id="L463"><td><a href="#L463">463</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: Kirk goes to the door and gestures for everyone to leave.</td></tr>

<tr id="L464"><td><a href="#L464">464</a></td><td>KIRK:  Gentlemen.</td></tr>

